using graphics lib, turtle lib

	'the window' : the graphics panel
	'turtle space' : a turtle space in 'the window'

	'turtle' : a turtle
	place 'turtle' in 'turtle space'
	'turtle' speed 100

	'turtle' random walk

	'turtle' random walk :
		repeat 100 times
			'turtle' colour (random colour)
			move 'turtle' to (random turtle point)
